summary: Boutique software agency located in Irvine, Caliornia
highlights: Reduced turn-around time by 15% by establishing clear communication protocols between engineering and business stakeholders.
Played primary role of interfacing between software engineers and business end users.
Actively participated in assessing the risks of various solutions and prioritizing competing business demands.
Collaborated and supported testing/QA team in the development and execution of test plans.
